tests.sic.sST.norm

Class sSTCnormSimpleHeurOpt

  • java.lang.Object
    • tests.sic.sST.norm.sSTCnormSimpleHeurOpt
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    OptimizerIntf

    public final class sSTCnormSimpleHeurOpt
extends java.lang.Object
implements OptimizerIntf
    class computes an approximate solution to the (s,S,T) policy optimization under normal demands, by computing the optimal (r,nQ,T) policy parameters r*,Q*, and T* using the algorithm implemented in class tests.sic.rnqt.norm.RnQTCnormOpt and then setting s=r*, S=r*+Q* and T=T*.

    Notes:

    • 2023-07-06: multiple threads cannot concurrently run the minimize(f) method.

    Title: popt4jlib

    Description: A Parallel Meta-Heuristic Optimization Library in Java

    Author:
